OL,3,CChild rapist jailed for 27 years in
OL,4,C'highly disturbing' case
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 27 years
OL,7,Fafter sexually abusing and raping
OL,8,Fchildren.
OL,10,FMarc Bear, from Launceston in
OL,11,FCornwall, was also given a year on
OL,12,Fextended licence, a Sexual Harm
OL,13,FPrevention Order and will be on the
OL,14,FSex Offenders Register for life.
OL,16,FThe 38-year-old was sentenced on
OL,17,FThursday 5 December at Truro Crown
OL,18,FCourt where the Judge told him that he
OL,19,Fwould be a risk to children for the
OL,20,Frest of his life.
