OL,3,CChild rapist jailed for 27 years in
OL,4,C'highly disturbing' case
OL,6,FFollowing a trial which ended in
OL,7,FNovember, a jury found Bear guilty of
OL,8,F16 offences against children including
OL,9,F10 counts of rape, two counts of
OL,10,Fsexual assault, two counts of causing
OL,11,For inciting a child to engage in
OL,12,Fsexual activity and two counts of
OL,13,Fcasing a person to engage in sexual
OL,14,Factivity.
OL,16,FThey also found Bear not guilty of two
OL,17,Foffences of causing or inciting a
OL,18,Fchild to engage in sexual activity,
OL,19,Fone count of rape and one count of
OL,20,Fsexual assault.
