OL,3,CChild rapist jailed for 27 years in
OL,4,C'highly disturbing' case
OL,6,FFollowing conviction, the judge
OL,7,Fgranted Bear bail in order to prepare
OL,8,Ffor a custodial sentence, however he
OL,9,Fabsconded and was found the following
OL,10,Fday in Somerset.
OL,12,FThe judge told him it was clear he had
OL,13,Fplanned to abscond, saying: "That told
OL,14,Fme everything I need to know about
OL,15,Fyour character."
