OL,4,C'highly disturbing' case
OL,6,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Tim Barbery from the Public
OL,8,FProtection Unit at Devon and Cornwall
OL,9,FPolice said: "This was a highly
OL,10,Fdisturbing case where the offender has
OL,11,Fexploited the vulnerability of young
OL,12,Fpeople for his own sexual
OL,13,Fgratification, and I welcome the
OL,14,Fsentence handed down by the judge.
OL,16,F"This has been a protracted
OL,17,Finvestigation due to the nature of the
OL,18,Foffences and the strength and bravery
OL,19,Fshown by the victims in support of the
OL,20,Fpolice case has been crucial.
